rows.label: tlk4730016801_msg0001
rows.name:
Eyup, pal!
I'm wondering what we're supposed
to do with this building here.

rows.label: tlk4730016801_msg0002
rows.name:
It's looking the worse for wear, so it
needs repairing, that's for sure. The
question is, how?

rows.label: tlk4730016801_msg0003
rows.name:
Could use it for storage, but it's a bit of
a waste. Thing is, if we turn it into a
house, then there's no one to live in it!

rows.label: tlk4730016801_msg0004
rows.name:
Unless of course you decided to
settle down with a nice lass, Rex.
That'd solve all our problems!
